    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "44a076c9-fc67-49d9-91b0-4322431b6821",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Some good cocaine a day keeps 47 away",
        "Location": "LOCATION_EDGY_FOX",
        "PublicId": "129843661476",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository f08fa211-e5e8-4406-9381-2f32dd16bd30).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning 47! Our client, a local drug lord, is not pleased with the local biker gang supplying him with the cocaine. According to him they have become lazy with their quality check and are delivering bad cocaine. He has requested that the guys make the cocaine to be eliminated. Also, the agency does not want you to become lazy as well and therefore you are to practice all your skills as well as to leave no trace of your visit. I&apos;ll leave you to prepare",
